      "message": "i think condition should be either status, regardless of toggle (i.e. `jobStatus in [FAILED, FAILED_AND_PAUSED, COMPLETED_WITH_ERRORS]`)\n\nthus, the toggle will only affect the possibility to get into a \"FAILED_AND_PAUSED\" state. but retry may be possible for both.\n\nalso, with this code you will disable retry for historic sessions which completed with \"COMPLETED_WITH_ERRORS\".",
